# ============================================
# OPTIONAL: Password Protection for Edit Pages
# ============================================
#
# By default, edit pages (/resume/edit, /cover-letter/edit) are publicly accessible.
#
# To ENABLE password protection:
# 1. Generate hash: node scripts/generate-password-hash.js "your-password"
# 2. Uncomment and set the variable below with your hash
# 3. For production: Add to GitHub Secrets as NEXT_PUBLIC_EDIT_PASSWORD_HASH
#
# To DISABLE password protection:
# - Simply comment out or remove this variable
# - Edit pages will be accessible without authentication
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_EDIT_PASSWORD_HASH=your-bcrypt-hash-here
